{"data": [{"id": "4741570", "title": "Agree Realty: 3 Reasons To Sell And Buy Realty Income", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173613768/image_173613768.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt='cat: don\"t look back in anger' data-id=\"173613768\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1152px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173613768/image_173613768.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173613768/image_173613768.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173613768/image_173613768.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173613768/image_173613768.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173613768/image_173613768.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173613768/image_173613768.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173613768/image_173613768.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173613768/image_173613768.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\">Our Cat Does Not Like The Valuation On Agree Realty</p> <p class=\"item-credits\">izold/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Our <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/author/trapping-value/analysis?ticker=ADC\">previous takes</a> on <b>Agree Realty Corporation</b> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ADC\" title=\"Agree Realty Corporation\">ADC</a></span>) have been on the neutral side, and we have only come away with a \u201chold\u201d rating. The stock</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173613768/image_173613768.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741570-agree-realty-3-reasons-to-sell-and-buy-realty-income", "pub_date": "2024-12-02 23:03:25"}, {"id": "4741568", "title": "Joby Aviation: How The Toyota Partnership Brings More Than Just Funding", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1399906856/image_1399906856.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Future mode of transport with electric and unmanned vehicles\" data-id=\"1399906856\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"864px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1399906856/image_1399906856.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1399906856/image_1399906856.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1399906856/image_1399906856.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1399906856/image_1399906856.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1399906856/image_1399906856.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1399906856/image_1399906856.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1399906856/image_1399906856.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1399906856/image_1399906856.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">mikkelwilliam</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Joby Aviation's stock (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/JOBY\" title=\"Joby Aviation, Inc.\">JOBY</a></span>) is still on the rise amid the current investor excitement in the eVTOL space, despite some uncertainties around the exact timeline for its FAA type rating approval.</p> <p></p> <p>Since the release of <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/filing/9216762\">Q3 earnings results</a></p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1399906856/image_1399906856.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741568-joby-aviation-toyota-partnership-brings-more-than-just-funding", "pub_date": "2024-12-02 23:00:14"}, {"id": "4741564", "title": "New Import Tariffs Will Be Bad For Ford But I Remain Bullish", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1392303787/image_1392303787.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Dealership of the multinational automobile company Ford\" data-id=\"1392303787\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1141px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1392303787/image_1392303787.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1392303787/image_1392303787.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1392303787/image_1392303787.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1392303787/image_1392303787.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1392303787/image_1392303787.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1392303787/image_1392303787.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1392303787/image_1392303787.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1392303787/image_1392303787.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Neme Jimenez/iStock Editorial via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>There is no shortage of challenges facing Ford Motor Company (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/F\" title=\"Ford Motor Company\">F</a></span>). Whenever things started to look promising in the last three years, Ford faced a new challenge. Donald Trump's thumping victory in the 2024 Presidential election seems to have unlocked a</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1392303787/image_1392303787.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741564-new-import-tariffs-will-be-bad-for-ford-but-i-remain-bullish", "pub_date": "2024-12-02 22:45:42"}, {"id": "4741563", "title": "GameStop: Is This Time Different?", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303187579/image_1303187579.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"GameStop store sign\" data-id=\"1303187579\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"3975px\" height=\"2650px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303187579/image_1303187579.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303187579/image_1303187579.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303187579/image_1303187579.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303187579/image_1303187579.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303187579/image_1303187579.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303187579/image_1303187579.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303187579/image_1303187579.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303187579/image_1303187579.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Dennis Diatel Photography</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>\"This time is different\" could be the four most dangerous words in trading. Markets rarely change. However, I have noticed a different pattern of behaviour in GameStop (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/GME\" title=\"GameStop Corp.\">GME</a></span>) as it is making a more sustained uptrend rather than the</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303187579/image_1303187579.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741563-gamestop-is-this-time-different", "pub_date": "2024-12-02 22:38:17"}, {"id": "4741577", "title": "United Back To Flying The Friendly Skies", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1321504180/image_1321504180.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Aerial shot showing an aircraft shadow flying over an idyllic beach scene, Barbados\" data-id=\"1321504180\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5464px\" height=\"3640px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1321504180/image_1321504180.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1321504180/image_1321504180.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1321504180/image_1321504180.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1321504180/image_1321504180.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1321504180/image_1321504180.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1321504180/image_1321504180.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1321504180/image_1321504180.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1321504180/image_1321504180.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Abstract Aerial Art</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Shares of United Airlines Holdings (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/UAL\" title=\"United Airlines Holdings, Inc.\">UAL</a></span>) have surged over 25% in the last month taking their YTD gain to an incredible 140%. Last week, the stock even briefly traded above $100 to new all-time highs. As shown in the chart</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1321504180/image_1321504180.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741577-united-back-to-flying-the-friendly-skies", "pub_date": "2024-12-02 22:30:00"}, {"id": "4741574", "title": "DXY's Rise Amidst Trump's BRICS Warning And French Uncertainty", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810122/image_1445810122.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Money on the edge\" data-id=\"1445810122\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"986px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810122/image_1445810122.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810122/image_1445810122.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810122/image_1445810122.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810122/image_1445810122.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810122/image_1445810122.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810122/image_1445810122.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810122/image_1445810122.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810122/image_1445810122.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">PM Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>By Zain Vawda</em></p> <p>The US Dollar kicked December off on the front foot as market participants digested comments from US President-elect Donald Trump. This is the second week that markets have taken their cue from Trump's comments to</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810122/image_1445810122.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741574-dxys-rise-amidst-trumps-brics-warning-and-french-uncertainty", "pub_date": "2024-12-02 22:17:00"}, {"id": "4741572", "title": "China's Export Tax Rebate Shock: The Aluminum Market Faces A New Reality", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/674830596/image_674830596.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"detail shot of extruded aluminum industry in a plant\" data-id=\"674830596\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/674830596/image_674830596.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/674830596/image_674830596.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/674830596/image_674830596.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/674830596/image_674830596.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/674830596/image_674830596.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/674830596/image_674830596.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/674830596/image_674830596.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/674830596/image_674830596.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">fanjianhua/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><a href=\"https://agmetalminer.com/2024/12/02/china-export-tax-price-of-aluminum/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><em>Original Post</em></a></p> <p><em>By Stuart Burns</em></p> <p>A much-reported but little-understood development in the aluminum market this month has the potential to significantly alter the supply chain landscape for aluminum semi-finished metals in the year ahead. Beyond that, it</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/674830596/image_674830596.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741572-china-export-tax-rebate-shock-aluminum-market-faces-new-reality", "pub_date": "2024-12-02 22:15:00"}, {"id": "4741565", "title": "Summit Therapeutics Stock Set To Soar By Mid-2025 On HARMONi Phase 3 Trial", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1595721515/image_1595721515.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Close-up view of Mount Everest\" data-id=\"1595721515\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1595721515/image_1595721515.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1595721515/image_1595721515.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1595721515/image_1595721515.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1595721515/image_1595721515.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1595721515/image_1595721515.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1595721515/image_1595721515.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1595721515/image_1595721515.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1595721515/image_1595721515.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\">The Summit of Mount Everest</p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Karin Dohmen/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><b>Summit Therapeutics Inc.</b> (NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SMMT\" class=\"ticker-link\">SMMT</a>) reached an important milestone in October, <a href=\"https://www.smmttx.com/pressrelease/promising-anti-tumor-activity-and-safety-of-ivonescimab-in-combination-therapies-in-crc-tnbc-and-hnscc-featured-at-esmo-2024-3/\" rel=\"nofollow\">completing enrollment</a> of its Phase III <a href=\"https://clinicaltrials.gov/study/NCT06396065?term=HARMONi&amp;rank=1\" rel=\"nofollow\">HARMONi</a> trial. Importantly, this study received <a href=\"https://www.biospace.com/drug-development/summit-therapeutics-announces-completion-of-enrollment-in-its-phase-iii-harmoni-trial-in-2l-egfrm-nsclc\" rel=\"nofollow\">fast track</a></p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1595721515/image_1595721515.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741565-summit-therapeutics-stock-set-to-soar-mid-2025-harmoni-phase-3-trial", "pub_date": "2024-12-02 22:10:07"}, {"id": "4741557", "title": "Navitas Semiconductor: The Secret Ingredient To AI's Next Leap", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2170889984/image_2170889984.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Digital abstract CPU. AI - Artificial Intelligence and machine learning concept\" data-id=\"2170889984\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"864px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2170889984/image_2170889984.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2170889984/image_2170889984.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2170889984/image_2170889984.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2170889984/image_2170889984.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/217088